reviewText:
Independent flick well done.

Original story with interesting characters. The acting is solid all the way around and the story has nice twists on this simple plot.
Everyone in this story is a first class A-hole loser.  Strangely enough, you'll find  a little bit of yourself  in many of those warehouse dead-end job workers....a bad day at the office, every day!

Clerks on steroids!

Fun, over the top at times but what the hell that's what entertainment is all about ain'it?
